This paper focuses on multi-sensor perception and multi-object tracking in autonomous driving systems, which involves computer vision (CV) and robotics (RO) techniques. The paper also proposes a novel multi-modality fusion module, which involves machine learning (LG) and artificial intelligence (AI) techniques. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of deep representation in data association, which involves natural language processing (CL) techniques. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.RO, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.CL.
